  "texts": [
    "The developing solvents for tanshinones and salvianolic acids were petroleum ether: ethyl acetate: cyclohexane (4:3:2) and dichloromethane: trichloromethane: ethyl acetate: methanol: formic acid (4:6:8:1:4), respectively.",
    "The tanshinones and salvianoic acids were observed by an ultraviolet lamp under 254 nm.",
    "UPLC analysis was performed by UPLC system (LC-30A03030623), with the following system parameters: column temperature 30 °C; injection volume 10 μL; flow rate 0.3 mL/min; detection wavelength 254 nm.",
    "The mobile phase was acetonitrile (A) -0.01% formic acid in water (B).",
    "The gradient program was as follows: 90%-40% B for 0-5 min; 40%-20% B for 5-10 min; 20% B for 10-14 min; 20%-10% B for 14-17 min."
  ],
  "correct_citations": []
}